#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/uBJvbf0g9rcsYElcwZCMYU0Vrj8.jpg" group-title="|ES| ACCION/CRIMEN" tvg-type="movie" description="The high-profile case of serial killer Ludovic Chevalier has just gone to trial, and Kelly-Anne is obsessed. When reality blurs with her morbid fantasies, she goes down a dark path to seek the final piece of the case’s puzzle." year="2023-08-11" director="Stéphanie Gaudreau, Marie-Alexandre Kérouac, Pascal Plante" actors="Juliette Gariépy, Laurie Babin, Élisabeth Locas, Maxwell McCabe-Lokos, Natalie Tannous",Red Rooms (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1825942.mkv&play_token=1M0qm9mrSl&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/i6ZO28AmFatUHKwW3LYzBsJvUSs.jpg" group-title="|ES| ACCION/CRIMEN" tvg-type="movie" description="Al regresar de Afganistán, Jessica, una marine de Spec OPS, se encuentra en una guerra que nunca imaginó y descubre que los suburbios del centro de Estados Unidos han cambiado cuando su hermana de trece años, Aimee, es secuestrada por traficantes sexuales." year="2023-09-08" director="Lee Whittaker" actors="Jet Jandreau, Alison Jaye Horowitz, Ana Alexander, Eric Pierce, Jamie Timmons, Julien Cesario, Laur Allen, Terence J. Rotolo, Emma Malouff, Alondra Delgado",ES - El último disparo (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1814093.mkv&play_token=9lRBxZPU1z&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/Ah9H6Sj434nJiZpTPQrovHaEePV.jpg" group-title="|ES| ACCION/CRIMEN" tvg-type="movie" description="A group of righteous assassins called The Collective take aim at a highly sophisticated human trafficking ring backed by a network of untouchable billionaires. With their backs against the wall, The Collective has no choice but to put their most important mission in the hands of rookie assassin, Sam Alexander." year="2023-08-04" director="Tom DeNucci" actors="Lucas Till, Ruby Rose, Tyrese Gibson, Don Johnson, Mercedes Varnado",The Collective (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1811579.mkv&play_token=BIaTUBW3QL&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

