#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://pics.filmaffinity.com/il_colibri-535851656-mmed.jpg" group-title="|ES| DRAMA/ROMANCE/FAMILIA" tvg-type="movie" description="La película sigue la vida de Marco Carrera (Favino), al que todos sus conocidos apodan 'el colibrí', a lo largo de las décadas. Desde la playa en la que en su adolescencia Marco conoce a Luisa (Bérénice Bejo), la mujer que amará toda su vida; pasando por Roma, donde vivirá durante años junto a su esposa Marina (Kasia Smutniak) y su hija Adèle; y terminando en Florencia junto a su amigo el psicoanalista Daniele Carradori (Nanni Moretti), que le enseñará a hacer frente a los continuos cambios de rumbo y golpes del destino con el mejor de los ánimos." year="2022-10-14" director="Francesca Archibugi" actors="Pierfrancesco Favino, Kasia Smutniak, Bérénice Bejo, Laura Morante, Sergio Albelli, Alessandro Tedeschi, Benedetta Porcaroli, Massimo Ceccherini, Fotinì Peluso, Francesco Centorame",ES - El colibrí (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1809282.mkv&play_token=IwXOFxqLfX&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/qMJfrZwIskRs2dQB7pGAeArphBp.jpg" group-title="|ES| DRAMA/ROMANCE/FAMILIA" tvg-type="movie" description="On a cold winter's day in 1940, Jules and his family move to live with his uncle, mayor of a settler's village in northern Quebec. He is banned from school because of his rare skin disease. From that moment on, his greatest wish is to be cured. When his dog Spark runs away into the wild forest, Jules has no choice but to look for him. On his way, he meets Asha, a mysterious young indigenous girl. Together, they venture to the other side of the forest, where nature reveals itself full of life and secrets." year="2023-07-07" director="Sophie Farkas Bolla" actors="Alex Dupras, Gaby Jourdain, Kevin Papatie, Marilyse Bourke, Emmanuel Schwartz",Adventures in the Land of Asha (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1806292.mkv&play_token=qA4rFjaRd3&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/lpIoYLy0S3wIOKU8qbyYGa9Wg4h.jpg" group-title="|ES| DRAMA/ROMANCE/FAMILIA" tvg-type="movie" description="Diego, a Venezuelan urbanist, and Elena, a contemporary dancer from Barcelona, move to the United States with their approved visas to start a new life. Their intention is to boost their professional careers and start a family in 'the land of opportunities'. But upon entering New York airport's immigration area, they are taken to the secondary inspection room, where border officers will subject them to an unpleasant inspection process and a psychologically grueling interrogation." year="2023-06-16" director="Alejandro Rojas, Juan Sebastián Vásquez" actors="Alberto Ammann, Bruna Cusí, Ben Temple, Laura Gómez, Colin Morgan",Upon Entry (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1799692.mkv&play_token=SmtAKQEDvZ&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gyOsdiwOkaxOIhKkBwlIdcVcZmI.jpg" group-title="|ES| DRAMA/ROMANCE/FAMILIA" tvg-type="movie" description="An idealistic and passionate literature teacher in a suburban Brussels school becomes the target of intense hostility from students and colleagues tied to Islamic extremism when she chooses to help a teenage Muslim girl accused of homosexuality." year="2024-04-17" director="Jawad Rhalib, Maïmouna Bancel, Charlotte Cristin, Freddy Verhoeven, Catherine Grossen" actors="Lubna Azabal, Fabrizio Rongione, Catherine Salée, Babetida Sadjo, Johan Heldenbergh",Amal (2024)
