#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/ll3tEeNbNbagiA76JsfV0xJJmku.jpg" group-title="|ES| PELICULAS 2000/2010" tvg-type="movie" description="Follows the Walton family as they prepare enthusiastically for the annual Harvest Festival Fair on Walton Mountain in 1934, but their lives are dramatically changed after a young boy arrives." year="2022-11-20" director="Joe Lazarov" actors="Richard Thomas, Bellamy Young, Teddy Sears, Logan Shroyer, Britt George, Marcelle LeBlanc, Marilyn McCoo, Adam Boyer, Donovan Elmore, Charles Green",ES - Acción de gracias con los Waltons - (2022)
